				\begin{document}$${\mathrm{rDoC}} = {\int}_0^{\pi /2} {I(\chi )\sin \chi \,{\mathrm{{d}}}\chi }$$\end{document}. Film thicknesses were measured using an ellipsometer (M-2000-XI, J. A. Woollam Co., Inc). Spacing and coherence lengths for the J61 and m-ITIC were calculated from the (100) peaks by fitting Gaussian peaks to the 1D sector-averaged profiles (see Supplementary Table S4). Coherence lengths were calculated using the Scherrer equation59.
